These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, dressmaker
2 different pets are kept: goat, mouse
1. the dressmaker is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Job           | dressmaker | designer |
| Pet   | mouse     | goat  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: apricot, purple
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, motorbike
1. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the left of the person who likes apricot##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Color         | purple   | apricot      |
| Transport   | airplane | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, rock
There 2 different types of food: radish, potato
1. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the right of the person eating radish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| Music-Genre   | rock | r&b    |
| Food     | radish | potato |

 #################################

 
