.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-10::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: country, disco
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: october, december
1. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##5
2. the fan of country is somewhere to the right of the fan of disco##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | disco | country |
| Birthday     | december   | october    |

